Name: pythontidy2
Version: 0.1.5
Summary: Tidy Python Script
Home-page: https://github.com/xuboying/pythontidy2
Author: Boying Xu
Author-email: xuboying@gmail.com
License: BSD
Download-URL: https://github.com/xuboying/pythontidy2/releases/tag/0.1.5
Description: 
        pythontidy2
        ===========
        
        Usage
        ~~~~~
        
        .. code:: python
        
            python -m pythontidy2 [-t expandtabsize] script.py
        
        Installation
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        .. code:: python
        
            pip install pythontidy2
        
        Description
        ~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        Tidy python scripts
        
        Not compliant to PEP8
        
        Effect
        ~~~~~~
        
        From:
        
        .. code:: python
        
            list = [1, 2, {
               'Alicedefg': '2341',
               'Beth' : "c",
               'Cecil' : '3258',
            }, 4]
        
        To:
        
        .. code:: python
        
            list = [1, 2, {
                            'Alicedefg' : '2341',
                            'Beth'      : "c",
                            'Cecil'     : '3258',
                            }, 4]
        
        From:
        
        .. code:: python
        
            doc = ""
            long_variable = ((doc+'
        ') if doc else '')
            x = ""
        
        To:
        
        .. code:: python
        
            doc           = ""
            long_variable = ((doc + '
        ') if doc else '')
            x             = ""
        
        License
        ~~~~~~~
        
        BSD
        
Keywords: utility
